      "role": "user",
      "content": "a new path... how? there is no 'me' without that work. my whole identity was built into those theories. now it's just gone. i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize the person staring back. it's just a shell. trying to 'find a new path' feels like a lie. like i'm just playing pretend at being alive when the part that actually mattered is dead.",
